 href="javascript:void(0)">Searching...</a></li></ul></div></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><!-- End Sticky Menu --><!-- Mobile Menu --><div class="mobile-menu"><div class="menu-backdrop"></div><div class="close-btn"><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-times" style="font-weight: 100; font-size: 1rem;" aria-hidden="true"></i></span></div><nav class="menu-box"><div class="nav-logo"><a href="./"><img src="img/namegeshwaram-logo.svg" alt="Top School in Pune" title=""></a></div><div class="menu-outer"><!--Here Menu Will Come Automatically Via Javascript / Same Menu as in Header--></div></nav></div><!-- End Mobile Menu --><div class="nav-overlay"><div class="cursor"></div><div class="cursor-follower"></div></div></header><!-- End Main Header --><link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/css/pagePhp.css"><section class='about_01 pt-0 pb-0'><section class="banner-wrp_01"><div><div class="row"><div class="col-11 mx-auto"><h2 class="mb-2 slider-con-text text-center text-md-right text-white"> Facilities </h2></div></div></div></section><div class='container'><div class="row text-left my-5"><div class="col-12 p-md-0"><h2 class="main-title"> A CAMPUS DESIGNED TO <span class="main-title mb-1 brand-color2">INSPIRE AND EMPOWER</span></h2></div><div class="col-12 p-md-0"><p>At Nageshwaram Education World, education transcends academics, creating an exciting, caring and supportive space where students thrive and all-round development takes centre stage.</p><p>Nageshwaram education world, stands out as a haven of learning nestled in a picturesque and pollution-free environment. The campus provides a safe and nurturing space for students, complete with extensive facilities such as expansive playgrounds and state-of-the-art infrastructure that cater to holistic development.</p><p>The school places a strong emphasis on arts and creativity, with a dedicated focus on music, dance and visual arts. The amphitheatre serves as a vibrant hub for cultural and creative expressions, enriching the school’s vibrant atmosphere.</p><p>Apart from having elaborate facilities for indoor games, Nageshwaram education world boasts of multiple sporting facilities, including a swimming pool, grounds for hockey, football, tennis, basketball, volleyball, a fully equipped gymnasium and more, encouraging students to excel in physical fitness and teamwork. The school integrates technology into learning with and well-equipped computer labs, enabling modern and interactive pedagogy.</p></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center " id="laboratories"><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Labo-01.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Labo-02.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Labo-03.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/atl-i (1).png" /></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 p-lg-5"><h4>Laboratories</h4><p class="m-0"> As a part of the Atal Innovation Mission, our school has been selected as the nodal centre for Atal Tinkering Lab (ATL), a workspace for students, which is equipped with innovative tools and resources to inspire creativity, critical thinking, and hands-on learning. This helps develop curiosity, creativity and imagination in young minds. Skills such as design mindset, computational thinking, adaptive learning, physical computing are inculcated. Additionally, the school’s well-equipped science and computer labs provide students with hands-on experiences, allowing them to actively engage with scientific and technological concepts, conduct experiments and develop practical skills. </p></div></div></div><div class="col-12 flex-wrap-reverse"><div class="row align-items-center flex-wrap-reverse " id="library"><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 pl-lg-0"><h4>Library</h4><p class="m-0 pr-3"> At Nageshwaram education world, the library is more than just a repository of books. It is a vibrant hub of scholastic exploration and intellectual development. It is intended to kindle inquisitiveness and develop a love for reading among the students. </p><p class="m-0 pr-3">Our library celebrates a varied and wide-ranging assortment of books appealing to all age groups and interests. From classic literature and contemporary fiction to reference materials and academic resources, the collection is judiciously handpicked to underpin the school’s curriculum and inspire self-learning. The library also boasts of a wide array of magazines, journals and newspapers to keep the students updated with current national and international affairs and trends.</p></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Lib-01.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/lib-latest.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Lib-02.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Lib-03.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Lib-04.jpg" /></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center" id="sports"><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><!-- <div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Sports-01.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Sports-02.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Sports-03.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Sports-04.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/sports-i.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/sports-ii.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/sports-iii.png" /></div></div> --><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/sport-latest-i%20(3).png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/sports-latest (1).png" /></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 p-lg-5"><h4>Sports</h4><p class="m-0"> Nageshwaram education world emphasizes the role of physical activities and sports in promoting overall health and well-being. Engaging in sports contributes to physical fitness, mental resilience, emotional stability and social connectedness. </p><p class="m-0"> Apart from the elaborate amenities for indoor games, Nageshwaram education world boasts of multiple sporting facilities, including swimming pool, grounds for hockey, football, tennis, basketball, volleyball, a fully equipped gymnasium and more, encouraging students to excel in physical fitness and teamwork. </p></div></div></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center flex-wrap-reverse" id="jimmy"><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 pl-lg-0"><h4>Jimmy Jolley Park</h4><p class="m-0 pr-3"> In order to provide opportunities for physical and creative play, a simple and safe tyre park system for children has been developed. Tyre parks provide a play environment that promotes balance, coordination and the enhancement of gross motor skills. A child’s creativity can be seen best in the sand area. It helps augment psychomotor skills as well as social competence. Children are free to discover creative play methods and therby enhance cross-curricular linkage. </p></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="Best CBSE school in Patna" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Jim-01.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Jim-02.jpg" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Jim-03.jpg" /></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center" id="activity"><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/activity-i.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/activity-ii.png"/></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Activity-01.jpg"/></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Activity-02.jpg"/></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/Activity-03.jpg"/></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 p-lg-5"><h4>Activity Room</h4><p class="m-0"> The Activity Room supports holistic development of children by enhancing physical, cognitive, emotional and social skills through engaging activities. It is a place where ideas are brought to life, passions are discovered and students are inspired to think outside the box ensuring a well-rounded and enriching learning experience. It promotes learning through play, allowing children to explore, experiment, and grasp concepts interactively. Various areas set up in the room cater to diverse learning styles, providing every child an opportunity to thrive. It nurtures independence by offering choices and builds social skills through peer interaction and collaboration. </p></div></div></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center flex-wrap-reverse" id="dance"><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 pl-lg-0"><h4 class="pr-3">Dance & Music Studios</h4><p class="m-0 pr-3"> The Dance and Music Studios at Nageshwaram education world are dedicated spaces where students immerse themselves in the performing arts and discover their creative potential. Equipped with the latest facilities, these studios are designed to inspire and cultivate talent in a vibrant and supportive environment. </p><p class="m-0 pr-3"> These studios not only augment creative motor skills of the students, but also develops confidence in them, provide opportunities to collaborate and nurture an appreciation of the arts. Regular practice sessions and performance opportunities motivate the students to follow their artistic pursuits and shine in their area of interest. </p></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/dm-latest-I.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/dm-latest-II.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><!-- <img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/dm-latest.png" /> --><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/music&dance%20(1).png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><!-- <img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/dns-mu-01.jpg" /> --><img src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/music&dance-i%20(1).png" class="w-100 img-thumbnail" alt="Best CBSE school in Patna"></div><!-- <div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/img/dns-mu-02.jpg" /></div> --><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/dance-i.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/dance-ii.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="image" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/dance-iii.png" /></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-12"><div class="row align-items-center" id="tech"><div class="col-lg-6 p-0 m-0"><div class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly"><div class="carousel-inner"><div class="carousel-item active"><img alt="Best CBSE school in Patna" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/tech-i.png" /></div><div class="carousel-item"><img alt="Best CBSE school in Patna" class="w-100" src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpspatna/tech-ii.png" /></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 p-3 p-lg-5"><h4>Tech-Savvy Classes</h4><p class="m-0"> At Nageshwaram education world, technology plays an instrumental role in elevating the teaching and learning experience. To make the teaching-learning process student centric and multi-dimensional, the use of interactive panels has been incorporated. This has revolutionised traditional education into an engaging and dynamic process. Interactive panels are modern touchscreen devices integrated into classrooms to facilitate a collaborative and immersive learning environment. These panels serve as powerful tools for teachers to deliver lessons in visually appealing and interactive formats, making complex concepts easier to understand. </p><!-- <p class="m-0"></p><p class="m-0"></p> --></div><div class="col-12 px-3 pb-lg-3 pt-xl-4 px-lg-0 mt-xl-0"><p class="mb-0"> Teachers use multimedia content such as videos, animations and interactive diagrams to explain subjects more effectively. The touch-enabled panels allow students to actively participate in lessons through hands-on activities, quizzes, and games. These panels connect effortlessly with other devices, enabling teachers to share digital content, access online resources, and use educational apps. With features like annotation tools and virtual whiteboards, teachers can personalize lessons to cater to different learning styles. The panels provide instant access to a wealth of online educational resources, broadening the scope of classroom instruction. Teachers use interactive panels to create interactive lessons, quizzes and activities that encourage student participation, to share visually rich content, such as images, videos, and text, to have real-time collaboration, such as group activities, story writing and problem-solving exercises and to test student knowledge and quickly provide results.  With a strong focus on arts, sports, and technology, Nageshwaram education world nurtures creativity through music, dance, and visual arts, showcased in its vibrant amphitheatre. The campus includes top-tier sports facilities like Football, Basketball, Badminton, Table Tennis, Volleyball, Kho-Kho, Athletics, etc. promoting fitness and teamwork. Advanced ICT labs further enrich the academic experience through interactive, tech-integrated learning. </p></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></section><!--main content end //--><footer class="main-footer py-lg-2 py-3"><div class="container pt-md-4"><!--Widgets Section--><div class="row justify-content-between"><!--Column--><div class="col-lg-3 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 px-sm-0"><div class="widget contact-widget about-widget mb-4 mb-lg-0 ml-0"><div class="foot-logo"><a href="#"><img src="img/namegeshwaram-logo.svg" class="img-fluid mb-2" alt="footer_logo"></a><h3 class="widget-title mb-2">Nageshwaram education world</h3><p class="mb-1">Vill. Chandmari, P.S. Shahpur Danapur Cantonment Patna - 801 502</p><p class='mb-0'><img style='width: 24px;' src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshila/dpscoimbatore/call_01.svg" alt="Top School in Patna"><a class="footer-a" href="tel:+91 1234567890"> +91 1234567890</a></p><p class='mb-0'><img style='width: 24px;' src="https://resources.edunexttechnologies.com/web-data/takshil